<P>
   &LR; CHARLES M. SCHULZ, CREATOR OF BELOVED `PEANUTS,' DIES AT 77 &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR; A5729 Testwls &UR;  &LR;  7 20:44 R A  &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR; lslslslslsjujaldlkldzkLDjLDjzk &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR; A5713 BC-PEANUTS-TIMELINE14-COX-1STLEDE &UR;  &LR; 2208 20:35 U A  &UR;
