<HEADLINE>
NEWS OF THE WEEK IN REVIEW 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Slinging Mud Among the Palmettos
</P>
