<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-14 08:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6123 &Cx1f; taf-z
u x BC-BESTSELLERS-HARD-S-$A     02-14 1105
