<HEADLINE>
YOUNG AND ANARCHIC, THE ANGRY LEFT IS REBORN IN MEXICO 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 By JULIA PRESTON   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   MEXICO CITY _ During The Cold War, when Latin American leftists
