   Each week, we'd like to tell you a new joke, but we need your
help. Please e-mail us your best knee slappers, and we may run them
in the paper. Send your jokes and riddles to nfk(at)ajc.com. Here's
our first joke to get the ball rolling!
</P>
<P>
   Knock, knock.
</P>
<P>
   Who's there?
</P>
<P>
   Dwayne.
</P>
<P>
   Dwayne who?
</P>
<P>
   Dwayne the tub,
</P>
<P>
   I'm dwowning!
</P>
<P>
   _ Jordan Zemmin, 6,
</P>
<P>
   Freeman's Mill Elementary School,
</P>
<P>
   Gwinnett County
</P>
