<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TECH-WEBSHOP15-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Shopping on the Web
 &HT;    By Omar Gallaga
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _ www.seaside.net/phoneskins/ _ If you're tired of
your cell phone looking just like everybody else's, why not go for
a faux-leopard skin cover? Phone Skins offers phone covers for some
Motorola and Nokia phones. Give your phone a new attitude.
</P>
<P>
   MUST BUY: ``Furocious Kitty'' plush cover, $24.95 plus $4.95
shipping.
</P>
<P>
   www.1cache.com _ Those who know their electronics and don't need
a lot of hand-holding would do well to check out 1cache.com, one of
Yahoo's stores, dealing in no-frills gadget shopping. With minimal
design, but good deals, 1cache caters to those shoppers who don't
like being distracted while they shop. If you do need help, a 1-800
number is available to help on the fly.
</P>
<P>
   MUST BUY: Jensen CD-510K car CD player, $187.95 plus $8
shipping.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
<P>
   For Use By Clients of the New York Times News Service
</P>
