   BODIES-SIZES _ Bodies come in all shapes and sizes, but lots of
women find reasons not to like the size they're in. Some of those
women are captured in photographs _ beautiful bodies of women with
eating disorders _ by Holly Sasnett. We'll talk to her about what
the ``The Body Image Project'' is all about, how she was drawn to
it, what the women had to say about their photographs, how society
pushes women to conform to a thin body type. (Guthrie, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30. WITH PHOTOS.
