   PSYCHOLOGY-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ Is your Valentine your spouse?
If so, the following information might enrich or improve your
marriage. Judith S. Wallerstein, Ph.D., co-author of the book ``The
Good Marriage: How and Why Love Lasts,'' listed nine components for
a healthy marriage. (LeCrone, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED
</P>
