<P>
   TECH-ISMELL _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ It won't be long before
your computer is stinking up the joint. The iSmell _ no kidding,
that's its name _ is a boxy gizmo that looks like a pencil
sharpener and attaches to your computer like a printer. Inside is a
tray of scent materials, called a scent palate, that can produce
thousands of smells on command. (Crecente, Palm Beach Post) MOVED
</P>
