(Gallaga, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   TECH-KIDGEAR _ AUSTIN, Texas _ There are things to like about
the Simon &AMP; Schuster New Millennium Children's Encyclopedia and
Home Reference Library (Deluxe 2000 Edition; $21;
www.simonandschuster.com), but its giggly rainbow of typography and
``For Ages 8-12 Years'' on the cover belie its hard-to-fathom
interface and a dizzying array of options that will daunt most
adults and overwhelm its target audience. (Stafford, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   TECH-GAMER _ This week's rundown of software for the console and
