   &UR; CHINESE MEDICINE TRADE IS KILLING SEA HORSES &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A research team, Project Sea Horse, is working to counter the
threat to sea horses from habitat destruction, exploitation as
curios and, in particular, overfishing for traditional Chinese
medicine. Millions of dead sea horses pass every year through Hong
Kong, the main trading center. &QL;
