<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-14 13:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6416 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-JORDAN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      02-14 0852
