<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-14 13:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6443 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-ART-TATE-2TAKES-BOS &LR;      02-14 1225
