<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-14 16:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6553 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r t BC-TRAVEL-LASVEGAS-FINEA     02-14 0744
