<HEADLINE>
AMERICA'S TOP-SECRET `X FILES' AIR BASE EXPOSED  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This 500-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
