 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``p'' political news, ``a'' domestic news and ``k'' commentary news
files.)  
  
 By MARY DEJEVSKY  
 c.2000 The Independent, London  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ The lady may not bake cookies, but she tosses a
