<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-14 17:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6641 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r l BC-OLDER-YOUNGER-LADN &LR;      02-14 0681
