<P>
   &UR; AMERICA'S TOP-SECRET `X FILES' AIR BASE EXPOSED &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   These are the pictures that ``X Files'' fans the world over want
to see. Armed with the latest in high-powered cameras, two
plane-spotters have blown a hole through the U.S.'s strictest
security and revealed detailed shots of the legendary Area 51, a
top-secret military facility north of Las Vegas. So secret is the
base that the U.S. government denies its existence. But unlike
``The X Files,'' Area 51 is real. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By Paul Lashmar, The Independent of London &QL;
