to upgrade some P-3 Orion ocean patrol &UR;  &LR; aircraft after the defense
contractor fell behind schedule on the work. By Ross Kerber.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   AOL-CABLE (Undated) _ America Online halts lobbying for
legislation requiring cable firms to share high-speed Internet
lines with competitors. By Peter Howe. 600 words.
