covers of those magazines. ... Look at the covers of most of the
magazines and all the actresses look like porno stars. They're all
dropping their clothes. I'm always proud of Uma that at least it's
just her face on the cover of Elle magazine. It isn't her ass or
her nipples. It's very strange. You never saw Meryl Streep doing
that. You never saw Jessica Lange doing that.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Ethan Hawke, who is married to Uma Thurman, in the Times of
London.
