the processes of life. Incyte Pharmaceuticals in Palo Alto is an
example of this convergence between DNA and silicon. ``When you
think about it, biology is a very complex software system,'' says
Randy Scott, Incyte's chief scientist and co-founder. ``The genes
in your DNA encode the information for how to build a human
being.''  &UR; Column By TOM ABATE &LR;
