   - Movie critic  &UR; Jan Wahl  &LR; ran into  &UR; Bill Bradley &LR;  at KRON last
week and asked him about his favorite movies. His immediate first
choice: ``State of the Union,'' the  &UR; Frank Capra  &LR; movie that
starred  &UR; Spencer Tracy &LR;  and  &UR; Katharine Hepburn &LR; . The plot concerns
a Republican candidate who learns to speak out more strongly as his
campaign progresses.
</P>
