Siberian-born supermodel  &UR; Irina Pantaeva &LR;  told  &UR; Baird Jones  &LR; that
 &UR; Jay McInerney  &LR; has been working on a screenplay about her life. She
said she would like  &UR; Natalie Portman &LR;  to play her as a young
person, ``and then to play me in my 40s, I think  &UR; Catherine &LR; 
 &UR; Zeta-Jones &LR;  would be perfect.'' Zeta-Jones is 30.
