A group of people, some students at Columbine High School, stand
near a Subway sandwich shop where two students were killed, Monday.
Tragedy struck Columbine High School for the second time within a
year Moday when two sophomores were found shot to death in the
sandwich shop a short distance from the school where a 1999
massacre left 15 people dead. (Kevin Moloney/The New York Times)
</P>
